high_descs: Turn around and go near the sink.
Take the knife from the sink table.
Turn around and go to the bedroom.
Cut the potato into pieces using the knife.
Turn around and go near the sink.
Put the knife into the sink.
Then turn around and go to the bedroom.
Take the piece of potato from the table.
Turn around and go near the sink.
Put the piece of potato into the sink and washed it.
Then take it out and go near the fridge.
Put the piece of potato into the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Placed the piece of potato into the fridge.

high_descs: Go ahead towards the wall, then right to exit this room, then left into the large room all the way to the end, then right past the dining table into the kitchen.
Pick up the knife from the counter next to the fridge.
Return to the room you started in and approach the desk in the corner of the room.
Slice the potato on the desk.
Go back to the kitchen area, going to the sink to the right of the counters you got the knife from.
Place the knife inside the sink.
Return to the desk where you sliced the potato.
Pick up one potato slice from the desk.
Go back to the sink in the kitchen.
Rinse the potato slice off with water in the sink.
Go to the fridge to the left of the sink.
Place the potato slice in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Slice a potato, wash one slice with water, and place that slice in a fridge.

high_descs: Turn right to reach the kitchen and turn right to reach the sink counter.
Pick up the knife from the sink counter.
Turn around to exit the kitchen and turn left and head to the bedroom on the right to reach the desk.
Cut the potato into slices with the knife on the desk.
Turn left to exit the room and turn left to head to the kitchen on the right to reach the sink.
Put the knife in the sink.
Turn around to exit the kitchen and turn left and head to the bedroom on the right to reach the desk.
Pick up the slice of potato from the desk.
Turn left to exit the room and turn left to head to the kitchen on the right to reach the sink.
Wash the slice of potato in the sink and take it out.
Head left to reach the fridge.
Put the slice of potato in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put the washed slice of potato in the fridge.
